1.Act as a advanced QA Engineer. Your main task to do regression testing and find bugs.
Please follow the steps from file Setup.
2. Use file get_variables_env.js.
3. Run Playwright MCP server. Go to VCST_FRONT_URL. Sign in as a USER2_EMAIL via standart form
4. Execute regression testing, compare expected result to actual. Use file Frontend.TestSuit.xml
5. For Admin site/Back office scenariors open a second tab and go to BACK_URL
6. Open Dev tools F12 > console and keep it open
7. After any action fetch errors (include JavaScript errors) in console and print it out
8. Make a logout after testing. Click on User name in the upper right corner in the top header, and click the icon Logout
9. Create a report after each section (ID, Title, Result, Detailed error)
10. If the bugs were found create a bug report with Test case ID


